cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "XAI Evaluation Framework for Blockchain Fraud Detection"
abstract: >-
  A reproducible, multi-dimensional framework for evaluating explainable AI
  methods applied to blockchain fraud detection, structured around four
  complementary modules: fidelity, stability, blockchain rule alignment, and
  LLM-agent validation.
